title: Peter Strzok, "Compromised: Counterintelligence and the Threat of Donald J. Trump"
description:
Former FBI Deputy Assistant Director of Counterintelligence Peter Strzok details his career & work on the FBI investigation into Russia’s interference in the 2016 election. He’s interviewed by the Adam Goldman of the New York Times.
